---
// About Page - Preserved Legacy Frontend Design
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Xiaoyou Wu" description="Learn about Xiaoyou Wu's journey in computer engineering, passion projects, and vision for the future of technology.">
  <div class="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      
      <div class="about-content">
        <a class="question">
          <p>
            Why on earth we have both profile tab and about me tab?
          </p>
        </a>
        <a class="answer">
          <p> 
            This one is about the non-academic part of me ~
          </p>
        </a>
        <a class="quote">
          <p>
            It is my good fortune to have been born of the coast, and to have known since childhood that so much of this world is consumed by a ceaseless, reciprocal devouring. Some of this feasting is soundless, as it is with the day and the night. Not a whimper escapes their lips, yet their eternal clash bleeds out across the sky as the crimson blush of dawn and dusk. But other conflicts cannot conceal their choked cries and lamentations—so it is with the ocean and the land. Where the sea and the earth meet, there is ever an overwhelming, sorrowful chorus that fills all space.
          </p>
        </a>
        
        <h2 class="difference-section">What makes me different ?
          <p class="difference-content">
            I was born with a defect that after meeting a person or even knowing a person a fairly long time, I can't perfectly reconstruct their face. But I can still recognize them in a crowd. 
            This structural difference enable me to appreciate the beauty of blurriness. By blurriness, I mean I get to awe at something without digging into the details. 
            For engineers, the beauty originated from the understanding of the minutiae, the enlightenment that happens when the details are revealed. But, for me, the beauty can also lay on the fact of not revealing the details, just let the incredible engineering work stay there and I get to appreciate it all day.
            Therefore, I'm more interested in architectural designs and systems, and able to generate unique perspectives towards architectures.
          </p>
        </h2>

        <h2 class="passion-section">Passion I have ?
          <p class="passion-content">
              Raps ~
              Writing magic realistic short stories in Chinese ~
              Studying philosophy and psychology ~
          </p>
        </h2>

        <p class="closing-message">
          Thank you for taking the time to learn about my story. I'd love to connect with fellow engineers, 
          researchers, and anyone passionate about technology and innovation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* About Page Styles - Preserved from Legacy Frontend */
  .about {
    background-color: #F4E8D1;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    padding: var(--section-spacing) 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Premium heading with luxury styling - Preserved */
  .about h1 {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    animation: titleReveal 1.2s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes titleReveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-30px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Elegant heading underline - Preserved */
  .about h1::after {
    background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold-light));
    bottom: -10px;
    content: '';
    height: 3px;
    left: 50%;
    position: absolute;
    transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(0);
    width: 80px;
    animation: underlineGrow 0.8s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes underlineGrow {
    0% {
      transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(0);
    }
    100% {
      transform: translateX(-50%) scaleX(1);
    }
  }

  /* Decorative elements - Preserved */
  .about::before {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-gold), transparent);
    content: '';
    height: 120px;
    left: 20px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    width: 3px;
    animation: slideDown 1.5s ease-out;
  }

  .about::after {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--color-gold));
    content: '';
    height: 120px;
    right: 20px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    animation: slideUp 1.5s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideDown {
    0% {
      height: 0;
    }
    100% {
      height: 120px;
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideUp {
    0% {
      height: 0;
    }
    100% {
      height: 120px;
    }
  }

  /* Content container with premium styling - Preserved */
  .about-content {
    background-color: var(--color-card-bg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
    margin: 2rem auto;
    max-width: 850px;
    padding: var(--card-padding);
    position: relative;
    transition: var(--transition-standard);
    animation: contentFadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  @keyframes contentFadeIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .about-content:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
  }

  /* Elegant side accent - Preserved */
  .about-content::before {
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-gold), var(--color-gold-light));
    content: '';
    height: 100%;
    left: 0;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    width: 4px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg) 0 0 var(--border-radius-lg);
    animation: accentGrow 1.2s ease-out 0.8s both;
  }

  @keyframes accentGrow {
    0% {
      height: 0;
    }
    100% {
      height: 100%;
    }
  }

  /* Question styling - curious and inquisitive */
  .question {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f4fd, #f0f9ff);
    border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: questionPulse 2s infinite;
  }

  .question::before {
    content: "?";
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 15px;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #3b82f6;
    font-weight: bold;
    animation: questionMark 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .question:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #eff6ff);
  }

  .question p {
    color: #1e40af;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @keyframes questionPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
    }
  }

  @keyframes questionMark {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg);
    }
    25% {
      transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg);
    }
    75% {
      transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    }
  }

  /* Answer styling - gentle and revealing */
  .answer {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4, #f7fee7);
    border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    animation: answerReveal 0.8s ease-out 0.5s both;
  }

  .answer::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    top: -8px;
    right: 15px;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #22c55e;
    font-weight: bold;
    animation: checkMark 1s ease-out 1s both;
  }

  .answer:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dcfce7, #f0fdf4);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
  }

  .answer p {
    color: #15803d;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @keyframes answerReveal {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-30px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes checkMark {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }

  /* Quote styling - literary and flowing */
  .quote {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdf4ff, #faf5ff);
    border: 2px solid #a855f7;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    animation: quoteFadeIn 1s ease-out 1s both;
  }

  .quote::before {
    content: "Quote from me";
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 20px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #a855f7;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 1;
    animation: quoteFloat 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .quote::after {
    content: "Quote from me";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px;
    right: 20px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    color: #a855f7;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 1;
    animation: quoteFloat 3s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
  }

  .quote:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e8ff, #faf5ff);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15);
  }

  .quote p {
    color: #7c3aed;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.8;
    text-align: justify;
    margin: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @keyframes quoteFadeIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.95);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }

  @keyframes quoteFloat {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
  }

  /* Difference section - unique and blurred effect */
  .difference-section {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: sectionSlideIn 0.8s ease-out 1.5s both;
  }

  .difference-section:hover {
    transform: translateX(10px);
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .difference-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed, #ffedd5);
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    animation: contentBlur 0.8s ease-out 2s both;
  }

  .difference-content:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fff7ed);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @keyframes contentBlur {
    0% {
      filter: blur(2px);
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    100% {
      filter: blur(0px);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  /* Passion section - energetic and vibrant */
  .passion-section {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
    animation: passionPulse 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .passion-content {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2, #fce7e7);
    border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    animation: passionGlow 1s ease-out 2.5s both;
  }

  .passion-content:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2, #fef2f2);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  @keyframes passionPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
    }
    50% {
      text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.5);
    }
  }

  @keyframes passionGlow {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    }
  }

  /* Closing message - warm and inviting */
  .closing-message {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc, #f1f5f9);
    border: 2px solid #64748b;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
    animation: messageWave 1s ease-out 3s both;
  }

  .closing-message:hover {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2e8f0, #f8fafc);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  @keyframes messageWave {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes sectionSlideIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-50px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }
  }

  .about h2 {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about h2::after {
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
    bottom: -5px;
    content: '';
    height: 2px;
    left: 0;
    position: absolute;
    width: 60px;
    animation: underlineSlide 0.6s ease-out 0.3s both;
  }

  @keyframes underlineSlide {
    0% {
      width: 0;
    }
    100% {
      width: 60px;
    }
  }

  .about p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-family: var(--font-accent);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .about a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    position: relative;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition-standard);
  }

  .about a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-light);
  }

  .about a::after {
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
    bottom: -2px;
    content: '';
    height: 1px;
    left: 0;
    position: absolute;
    transition: var(--transition-standard);
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about a:hover::after {
    background-color: var(--color-gold-light);
  }

  /* Responsive adaptations - Preserved */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about {
      padding: 2.5rem 0;
    }
    
    .about h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
    }
    
    .about h2 {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
    }
    
    .about-content {
      padding: 2rem;
      margin: 1.5rem;
    }

    .quote::before,
    .quote::after {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    
    .about h1 {
      font-size: 2.4rem;
    }
    
    .about h2 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
    
    .about p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .about-content {
      padding: 1.8rem;
      margin: 1rem;
    }

    .quote::before,
    .quote::after {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style> 